OL,5,GThere was an awkward moment at the
OL,6,Gstart of the weather segment on the BBC
OL,7,GNews at One today, when a studio guest
OL,8,Ggot in the way of the camera shot.
OL,10,FEconomics correspondent Andy Verity was
OL,11,Fseated at the Studio E desk for a brief
OL,12,Fdiscussion with presenter Jane Hill on
OL,13,Fthe programme's final story.
OL,15,FDiscussion complete and it was time to
OL,16,Fpop across to the catwalk for the
OL,17,Fweather, with Tomasz Schafernaker.
