OL,5,FAs usual, when we transition to the
OL,6,Fweather segment, we get a wide shot of
OL,7,Fthe studio. But something's not quite
OL,8,Fright.
OL,10,FThe floor manager is seen waving
OL,11,Ffrantically to catch Andy Verity's
OL,12,Fattention. Presumably she's been
OL,13,Finformed by the director that Andy is
OL,14,Fobstructing the camera shot of the
OL,15,Fweather presenter.
OL,17,FWhen we then cut to the weather camera,
OL,18,Fthe back of Andy's head is in shot.
OL,19,FAfter a few seconds, he moves out of
OL,20,Fthe way.
